data.description:
This charming house boasts several attractive features, including updated paint throughout, ceiling fans for added comfort, and beautiful wood flooring in both the living room and bedrooms. 
The second living area offers versatility and can be used as an office, an extra bedroom, or even an additional living-dining space to suit your needs.
Step outside and discover the large backyard, providing ample space for relaxation and play. The garage, features built-in shelving, perfect for organizing and storing your belongings.
This home is brimming with potential and offers the perfect opportunity to kickstart the new year as a proud homeowner. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity, as homes like this tend to sell quickly. Get in touch with us today to schedule a viewing!
